frames.caption: A man in a uniform and a woman in a pink shirt stand closely together in a field of wildflowers, sharing a warm moment. The man wears a cap and a mask, while the woman gazes at him with a smile. The scene is set against a backdrop of lush greenery and colorful flowers.
